---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Creamy Pesto Dressing with Garlic Roast Veggie Salad
description: This is no ordinary schnitzel; tonight's golden crumbed chicken dish features a medley of roasted veggies and a drizzle of creamy pesto dressing for extra flair. With flavours like these, you won’t be missing your pub schnitty anytime soon!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65fcd2d10f30ef7affaa5361-3ba34f4b.jpeg
